text: Aschaffenburg (, East Franconian: ) is a Landkreis (district) in Bavaria, Germany. The district is located in the extreme northwest of Bavaria and bounded by Hesse on two sides. The Main river forms the western border. == Towns and municipalities == Towns: * Alzenau Municipalities: * Bessenbach * Blankenbach * Dammbach * Geiselbach * Glattbach * Goldbach * Großostheim * Haibach * Heigenbrücken * Heimbuchenthal * Heinrichsthal * Hösbach * Johannesberg * Kahl am Main * Karlstein am Main * Kleinkahl * Kleinostheim * Krombach * Laufach * Mainaschaff * Mespelbrunn * Mömbris * Rothenbuch * Sailauf * Schöllkrippen * Sommerkahl * Stockstadt am Main * Waldaschaff * Weibersbrunn * Westerngrund * Wiesen ==References==
